<bibRefCitation id="EFB807CC049715C4FE314B58FDF2FA78" author="Habe, T. &amp; Kosuge, S." box="[274,537,1393,1420]" pageId="158" pageNumber="159" refId="ref153761" refString="Habe, T. &amp; Kosuge, S. (1966) Shells in the World in colour. Vol. II. The Tropical Pacific. Hoisusha Publishing Co, Osaka, 193 pp." type="book" year="1966">Habe &amp; Kosuge (1966)</bibRefCitation>
