</taxonomicName>
is not available because it was introduced without a description of the species and of the characters to differentiate it from other taxa, but only with a figure (ICZN 
<collectingRegion id="49EDB4DF049715C4FE954BF7FE34FA0C" box="[438,479,1502,1528]" country="Djibouti" name="Arta" pageId="158" pageNumber="159">Art</collectingRegion>
. 13 (
<bibRefCitation id="EFB807CC049715C4FD374BF4FD4BFA03" author="ICZN" box="[532,672,1501,1527]" pageId="158" pageNumber="159" refId="ref155813" refString="ICZN (1999) International Code of Zoological Nomenclature 4 th Edition. The International Trust for Zoological Nomenclature, London, 306 pp." type="book" year="1999">ICZN, 1999</bibRefCitation>
)).
</paragraph>
